    num: "01",
    title: "Agent orchestration for a healthcare operations platform",
    kicker: "Healthcare",
    year: "2025",
    desc: "Built a multi-agent system that triages inbound clinical documents, extracts structured data, and routes cases through a review pipeline — replacing a manual queue that was choking a 120-person ops team.",
